From e2612f66120828c7615b6359f6b7b7f39e76c01d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mykola Hlukhenkyi <m.hlukhenkyi@inango-systems.com>
Date: Wed, 20 Aug 2025 15:04:26 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] miniupnpd: deprecated PortMapping Origin value

miniupnpd creates mappings with an outdated value for the Origin
parameter, which causes its rules to be excluded from the allowed and
the traffic mapping not to be applied.

Solution:
* Modified Origin value for PortMapping and InboundMapping entries from
  deprecated "UPnP_IWF" value to "UPnP"

References: PCF-2013

Signed-off-by: Mykola Hlukhenkyi <m.hlukhenkyi@inango-systems.com>
---
 miniupnpd/amx/amxpcp.c | 17 +++++++++--------
 miniupnpd/amx/amxpmp.c | 22 +++++++++++-----------
 miniupnpd/amx/amxrdr.c |  3 ++-
 3 files changed, 22 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)

